{"id": 6611, "title": "Ticket #6611: Update SlotType when schedd fakes up a dslot ad", "description": "<blockquote>\nWhen the schedd claims a partitionable slot (pslot), it fakes up the ad of the dynamic slot (dslot) that is created for the claim. It updates the <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=PartitionableSlot\" title=\"Partitionable Slot\">PartitionableSlot</a></span> and <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=DynamicSlot\" title=\"Dynamic Slot\">DynamicSlot</a></span> attributes (booleans). It should also update the <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=SlotType\" title=\"Slot Type\">SlotType</a></span> attribute (a string).\n\n<p>Yes, the schedd's fake dslot ad will always have inaccuracies and the real solution is for the startd to send the dslot ad, but the bad <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=SlotType\" title=\"Slot Type\">SlotType</a></span> value is tripping up users (CMS) and the fix is easy.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2018-Apr-02 11:04</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/38a47a2cadbb1606d070999b73bcd898b7cba8f6\">[54649]</a></span>: Docs for <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=SlotType\" title=\"Slot Type\">SlotType</a></span> bug fix in schedd's faked dslot ad. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6611\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6611'); return false;\" title=\"Update SlotType when schedd fakes up a dslot ad\">#6611</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td alig